me help
myself feel better naturally. Definitely 5 stars!”*Colin Reader

' | split: '|' %}

{% assign percents = 'Are satisfied with CuraLin*88.5%@width: 88.5%;
background: linear-gradient(
90.05deg
, #00D8C7 0%, #00B89D 100%);
|Feel safe using CuraLin*98.1%@width: 98.1%;
background: linear-gradient(
90.05deg
, #FACC37 0%, #F5A412 100%);
|Saw a big impact in their lives*84%@width: 84%;
background: linear-gradient(
90.05deg
, #FF90AC 0%, #FF5476 100%);
|Would recommend CuraLin to a friend*84%@width: 89%;
background: linear-gradient(
